data.description: Captivating 3BR, 2BA Home with Enchanting Landscaping in Oak Mountain School District  Nestled in Oak Mountain's premier school district, this charming 3-bed, 2-bath home invites you with a main-level master, gleaming hardwoods, and a partially finished basement. The allure extends outdoors with captivating landscaping, enhancing the beauty of the screened porch and deck in the fenced backyard. With low-maintenance brick/vinyl siding, this well-cared-for property seamlessly blends comfort and style. Don't miss the chance to call this enchanting home yours—schedule a viewing today!
